Subject:    Subnetting and in-addr.arpa domain, how ?
From:       <a href="?a=95837817000048&r=1&w=2">zaphod.mps.ohio-state.edu!usc!snorkelwacker!ira.uka.de!fauern!tumuc!lan!charly.b</a>
